    dc:title "Re-descriptions of eight chigger mite species (Acariformes: Trombiculidae) of the Leptotrombidium generic complex from Vietnam" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5591546>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5591548>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5591550> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5591546>
    dc:description "FIGURE 14. Leptotrombidium monstrosum (Schluger, 1960). A, dorsal aspect of idiosoma of lectotype (right sensillum lost); B, scutum of paralectotype ZMMU Tdt-3250, specimen 2 (left sensillum detached). Scale bars: 50 μm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5591546/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5591548>
    dc:description "FIGURE 15. Leptotrombidium monstrosum (Schluger, 1960). A, scutum of lectotype (right sensillum lost); B, humeral seta (C antero-marginal) of lectotype; C, dorsal idiosomal seta of lectotype; D, postanal seta of lectotype; E, preanal seta of lectotype; F, arrangement of dorsal idiosomal setae in paralectotype ZMMU Tdt-3244, specimen 1; G, ventral aspect of idiosoma in paralectotype ZMMU Tdt-3244, specimen 1. Abbreviations as in Fig. 2. Scale bars: 50 μm (A–E), 100 μm (F, G)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5591548/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5591550>
    dc:description "FIGURE 16. Leptotrombidium monstrosum (Schluger, 1960). A, ventral aspect of gnathosoma of lectotype (cheliceral blade lost); B, dorsal aspect of gnathosoma of lectotype (palpal claw broken); C, cheliceral blade; D, palpal claw; E, palpal claw (other side); F, leg I (trochanter–tarsus) of paralectotype ZMMU Tdt-3250, specimen 2; G, leg II (trochanter–tarsus) of paralectotype ZMMU Tdt-3250, specimen 2; H, leg III (trochanter–tarsus) of paralectotype ZMMU Tdt-3250, specimen 2 (one claw and empodium lost). Abbreviations as in Fig. 2. Scale bars: 50 μm (A–E), 50 μm (F–H)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5591550/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

